---
title: Thai Coconut Curry Chicken with Bell Pepper & Cilantro Lime Rice
description: This recipe is proof that a flavorful homemade curry can be just as easy as whipping up a grilled cheese or stir-fry for dinner. Chicken breast and bell pepper strips are seared until browned, then simmered in a creamy, dreamy coconut milk curry with Thai chili sauce and lime juice. Once the curry is thickened, the chicken is full of flavor, and the veggies are tender, it’s time to spoon everything over fluffy cilantro-lime rice and sprinkle with fresh cilantro and chili flakes for good measure. You can have all that in just 30 minutes—talk about game-changing dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5fea59f795e99a13fb4bddf0-5b405928.jpg
